===Pronunciation===
[[IPA]]: /lʊst/

===Noun===
'''lust''' ''m''
# [[desire]], [[pleasure]], [[appetite]], [[lust]]
#:''Him wæs metes micel lust'': he had a craving for food.  (Ælfric's ''Homilies'')

